## Overview

This service was created from the platform's golden-path template. It ships with
a health endpoint, a test suite, a container build, and continuous integration.

## Local development

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

The service listens on the port given by `PORT` (default `8080`). Probe
`GET /healthz` to confirm it is running.

## Continuous integration

Every push and pull request type-checks the code, runs the test suite, builds
the application, and verifies that the container image builds cleanly.
